OL,5, A postal worker is "living in fear"    
OL,6, over his credit rating after his bank  
OL,7, wrongly told him he was #1m overdrawn. 
OL,9,FBerkshire postie Azhar Bhutta realised 
OL,10,Fthere was a problem when he logged onto
OL,11,Fthe Barclays app on 13 June.           
OL,13,FIt suggested Mr Bhutta was overdrawn by
OL,14,F#498,764.27 while his savings account  
OL,15,Fwas #499,999.11 in the red.            
OL,17,FBarclays, which did not comment on the 
OL,18,Fcase, rectified the overdraft but      
OL,19,Fsuspended his accounts, leaving him    
OL,20,Fworried about defaulting on payments.  
